"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tShowing %(start)s to %(end)s of %(total)s projects\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t"
msgstr ""

#: templates/project_list.html:709
msgid ""
"Select a project package file (.zip) exported from another gvSIG Online "
"server."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un fichero de paquete de proyecto (.zip) exportado desde otro "
"servidor gvSIG Online."

#: templates/project_list.html:745
msgid ""
"Private project: export read/write/manage rules so they can be restored on "
"import."
msgstr ""
"Proyecto privado: exporta las reglas de lectura/escritura/gestión para que "
"puedan restaurarse en la importación."

#: templates/project_list.html:752
msgid ""
"Pack all raster files (GeoTIFF and associated auxiliary files) so they are "
"published automatically on import."
msgstr ""
"Empaqueta todos los ficheros ráster (GeoTIFF y ficheros auxiliares "
"asociados) para que se publiquen automáticamente en la importación."

#: templates/project_list.html:756
msgid ""
"Choose whether to copy data into the package (GPKG) or export metadata only "
"(destination must already have the tables)."
msgstr ""
"Elija si copiar los datos en el paquete (GPKG) o exportar solo los metadatos "
"(el destino debe tener ya las tablas)."

#: templates/project_list.html:788
msgid ""
"Building the ZIP file. This may take several minutes for large projects. "
"Please wait."
msgstr ""
"Generando el fichero ZIP. Esto puede tardar varios minutos en proyectos "
"grandes. Por favor, espere."

#: templates/project_package_export_result.html:24
msgid ""
"These layers are included in the package as metadata only (no GPKG data). "
"Check the technical log for details."
msgstr ""
"Estas capas están incluidas en el paquete solo como metadatos (sin datos "
"GPKG). Consulte el log técnico para más detalles."

#: templates/project_package_export_result.html:61
msgid ""
"No detailed log lines were recorded for this entry (older exports may lack "
"this)."
msgstr ""
"No se registraron líneas de log detalladas para esta entrada (exportaciones "
"antiguas pueden carecer de ellas)."

#: templates/project_package_import_wizard.html:101
msgid ""
"Layers from the local database are loaded into the original workspace and "
"datastore from the export (created automatically on this server if they do "
"not exist)."
msgstr ""
"Las capas de la base de datos local se cargan en el workspace y almacén "
"originales de la exportación (creados automáticamente en este servidor si no "
"existen)."

#: templates/project_package_import_wizard.html:137
msgid ""
"Data exported from a foreign database is loaded into the local CartoDB. "
"Choose an existing local CartoDB datastore on this server (workspace is "
"taken from the datastore). Foreign database datastores are not listed."
msgstr ""
"Los datos exportados de una base de datos externa se cargan en el CartoDB "
"local. Elija un almacén CartoDB local existente en este servidor (el "
"workspace se toma del almacén). Los almacenes de bases de datos externas no "
"aparecen en la lista."

#: templates/project_package_import_wizard.html:179
msgid ""
"These layers have no GPKG in the package. Map each connection to PostGIS on "
"this server, or check Skip to omit them (the rest of the project still "
"imports)."
msgstr ""
"Estas capas no tienen GPKG en el paquete. Asigne cada conexión a un PostGIS "
"en este servidor, o marque Omitir para excluirlas (el resto del proyecto se "
"importa igualmente)."

#: templates/project_package_import_wizard.html:215
msgid ""
"Check Skip to leave definition-only layers out (you can add them manually "
"later)."
msgstr ""
"Marque Omitir para dejar fuera las capas solo-definición (puede añadirlas "
"manualmente después)."

#: templates/project_package_import_wizard.html:220
msgid ""
"The following raster layers will be published automatically during import."
msgstr ""
"Las siguientes capas ráster se publicarán automáticamente durante la "
"importación."

#: templates/project_package_import_wizard.html:245
msgid ""
"The following external service layers will be imported as-is (no data is "
"copied)."
msgstr ""
"Las siguientes capas de servicios externos se importarán tal cual (no se "
"copia ningún dato)."

#: templates/project_package_import_wizard.html:278
msgid ""
"Loads GPKG into the target datastores, publishes layers, and creates the "
"project. Role permissions from the package are applied when present; "
"otherwise the project stays public."
msgstr ""
"Carga el GPKG en los almacenes destino, publica las capas y crea el "
"proyecto. Los permisos de roles del paquete se aplican si están presentes; "
"de lo contrario el proyecto queda público."

#: views.py:533
msgid ""
"Project imported with warnings. Some layers were skipped — see the import "
"report."
msgstr ""

#: views.py:604
msgid ""
"Project package import is not set up in the database. Run migrations on the "
"server (for example: python manage.py migrate gvsigol_project_package)."
msgstr ""

